 },
 {
  "text": "This is Sarah, my colleague.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a5_this_is_sarah_my_colleague.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Have you met my counterpart from Chicago?",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a5_have_you_met_my_counterpart_from_chicago.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "She leads the valuation team.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a5_she_leads_the_valuation_team.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "He manages our Chicago office.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a5_he_manages_our_chicago_office.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Marcos, it is good to see you again! Are you here with your team?",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a5_marcos_it_is_good_to_see_you_again_are_you_here.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "I am! My colleague Sarah is here too. This is her on the program -- she leads our valuation team.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a5_i_am_my_colleague_sarah_is_here_too_this_is_her.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Oh, so she leads the team? I would love to meet her. What does her team focus on?",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a5_oh_so_she_leads_the_team_i_would_love_to_meet_he.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "She focuses on industrial assets. Have you met my counterpart from Chicago, David? He manages your partner office there.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a5_she_focuses_on_industrial_assets_have_you_met_my.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "David! Yes, he is a mutual friend -- what a small world. It is a pleasure to discover we are connected.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a5_david_yes_he_is_a_mutual_friend_what_a_small_wor.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "It really is! Let me connect you with Sarah at lunch. I am sure you would love to get to know her.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a5_it_really_is_let_me_connect_you_with_sarah_at_lu.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "That would be wonderful. Please introduce us -- I will be at the lunch table by the window.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a5_that_would_be_wonderful_please_introduce_us_i_wi.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Perfect. On behalf of our team, thank you, Ellen. I will bring Sarah over and introduce you both.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a5_perfect_on_behalf_of_our_team_thank_you_ellen_i.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "She leads our valuation team.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a5_she_leads_our_valuation_team.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "It is a pleasure to meet you.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a5_it_is_a_pleasure_to_meet_you.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "I believe we have a mutual friend.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a5_i_believe_we_have_a_mutual_friend.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Ladies and gentlemen, it is my pleasure to introduce our next speaker. This is Doctor Helena Costa, and she leads one of the most respected valuation teams in the region. She manages large international projects, and she works closely with banks and investors across three continents. We have a mutual goal today: to make valuation clearer and more reliable for everyone. On behalf of the organizing committee, I would like to welcome her warmly to the stage. Please join me in giving a big round of applause. The floor is yours, Doctor Costa.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a5_listening_speaker.mp3"
 },
